             was indicted for <rs id="t18310217-168-off1010" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18310217-168-off1010" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310217-168-off1010" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
